high_descs: Turn left and face the back of the toilet.
Pick up the spray bottle on the right.
Walk to the sink to the left of the toilet.
Put the spray bottle down to the right of the sink.
Walk back over to the back of the toilet.
Pick up the remaining spray bottle.
Walk over to the front of the sink.
Put the spray bottle down to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move two spray bottles to the counter with the sink.

high_descs: Go forward to the shower, turn left, go forward to the toilet.
Take the right spray bottle from the toilet tank.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the sink, go forward to the sink.
Put the spray bottle to the right of the sink.
Turn around, go forward a step, turn left, go forward, turn left at the toilet.
Take the spray bottle from the toilet tank.
Go back in front of the sink.
Put the spray bottle to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles on the sides of a sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the toilet.
Pick up the right spray bottle from the tank.
Carry the bottle and turn to the left and then right to face the sink.
Place the bottle on the right side of the sink.
Take a few steps to the right to move to the toilet.
Pick up the spray bottle on the tank.
Move the spray bottle to the left and face the sink.
Place the bottle on the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles to the counter.
